        {
            "_id": "8BepGIHpY5yY5uZf",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/actions/TwoActions.webp",
            "name": "Ready... Fire!",
            "sort": 400000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "action"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 2
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The ulat-kini kidnappers draws or reloads their bows, crossbows, and slings, then launches a ranged attack in the form of a volley. This volley is a @Template[type:burst|distance:10] within 120 feet that deals @Damage[(2d8+4)[piercing]|options:area-damage] or @Damage[(2d8+4)[bludgeoning]|options:area-damage]{bludgeoning} damage with a @Check[reflex|dc:25|basic|options:area-effect] save. When the ulat-kini kidnappers is reduced to 2 or fewer segments, this area decreases to a @Template[type:burst|distance:5].</p>"
                },
                "publication": {
                    "license": "ORC",
                    "remaster": true,
                    "title": ""
                },
                "rules": [],
                "slug": null,
                "traits": {
